         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>School transport contract</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="60112000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The contracting authority wishes to appoint a supplier to provide the following bus/coach services:</P>
               <P>1. Students who reside outside the school’s catchment area;</P>
               <P>2. Boarding students based at the Heversham Boarding site;</P>
               <P>3. Occasional intersite transport between Heversham and Milnthorpe for exams and the school’s sports day – up to 34 days per year;</P>
               <P>4. Students who take part in after school activities, therefore requiring later transport than the end of the normal school day, will require access to buses home at 5:15 pm on Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday from Dallam School to Lancaster.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="EUR">1413250.00</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
